column2: SELECT m.plateifu, m.mangaid, m.objra AS ra1, m.objdec AS dec1, n.objid, n.distance, o.ra AS ra2, o.dec AS dec2, o.specObjID, o.type, o.u, o.g, o.r, o.i, o.z, o.err_u, o.err_g, o.err_r, o.err_i, o.err_z, o.calibStatus_u, o.calibStatus_g, o.calibStatus_r, o.calibStatus_i, o.calibStatus_z, o.extinction_u, o.extinction_g, o.extinction_r, o.extinction_i, o.extinction_z, o.petroMag_u, o.petroMag_g, o.petroMag_r, o.petroMag_i, o.petroMag_z into mydb.MaNGA_photometry_v3 from MyDB.MaNGA_Simard AS m CROSS APPLY dbo.fGetNearestObjEq (m.objra, m.objdec, #) AS n JOIN PhotoObj AS o ON n.objid = o.objid
